Class SpaceSearcher

java.lang.Object
  edu.ohiou.labimp.basis.ViewObject
      edu.ohiou.labimp.spacesearch.SpaceSearcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
Drawable2D, Viewable, Searchable, java.io.Serializable
public class SpaceSearcher
extends ViewObject
implements Searchable

Class SpeaceSearcher perfroms space search on a supplied Searchable objects. It provides implementation of generic psace search algorithms, like depth first, breadth first, bast first and A*.
